      "role": "Diagram_Editor",
      "action_type": "clarify",
      "utterance": "明白了。我理解为：User触发请求，Runner作为中间层，GoogleMaps负责调用API和本地处理，APIService是外部Google Maps API，CSVFile做持久化存储。这个结构对吗？",
